title: HodgePodge Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Asian, French, Fusion, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small, family-owned business with a constantly changing menu. On the standing menu, there are clearly labeled (VG) salads and edamame hummus for vegans, plus vegetarian sandwiches could possibly be made vegan, so vegans please inquire. At least once a week there is a vegan soup. Has a few gluten free choices.
